    "{Tsunagaru hazu to shinjiru yo kiseki no youna hikari ga}",
    "",
    "{Bokutachi wo maneki kotae no chikaku ni iru yotte}",
    "{Kanji sasete kureru no wa honnou tekina mono sa}",
    "{Sara ni...atsuku!}",
    "",
